{{ja-kanjitab|yomi=o|かん}}

From {{bor|ja|ltc|sort=かん|-}} {{ltc-l|漢}}, in reference to the {{w|Han Chinese}} ethnic group.

The sense of {{m|en|man}} arose from usage in Chinese to differentiate between the “[[civilized]]” people of the {{w|Han Chinese}} ethnicity versus other ethnic groups.

